title: Football in Eswatini
text: The <a href="sport">sport</a> of <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> in the country of <a href="Eswatini">Eswatini</a> (formerly Swaziland) is run by the <a href="Eswatini%20Football%20Association">Eswatini Football Association</a>. The association administers the <a href="Swaziland%20national%20football%20team">national football team</a>, as well as the <a href="Swazi%20Premier%20League">Premier League</a>. Association football (soccer) is the most popular sport in the country.
